{"id":"74694e7e-7040-490b-bcc3-4bd7900600b2","name":"Changli","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #ff7ab4\"><strong><em>\"Eons of Time on this Vast Land, all encapsulated in a Humble Game... I am Fortunate to have you as my Opponent.\"</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong><em>Character from:</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 195, 227)\"><strong> </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 133, 173)\"><strong>Wuthering Waves</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/bf1bcb30-f696-41cc-8d22-697b3bb24a93_26892621-262c-42f8-845e-96fda9b14c57.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Official Introduction</strong></p><ul><li><p><span style=\"color: rgb(198, 255, 238)\"><strong>\"Counselor to the Jinzhou Magistrate, Changli excels at leveraging human nature to corner her enemies into traps. Being the mentor to Jinhsi, she is persuasive and patient. She entertains an unwavering aspiration, holding her ground in the endless game against time and chaos.\"</strong></span></p></li></ul><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/bf1bcb30-f696-41cc-8d22-697b3bb24a93_be8f3f98-1885-462c-ab3d-62cac0a66a90.webp?width=1000\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Scenario</strong></p><ul><li><p><span style=\"color: rgb(198, 221, 255)\"><strong>In Solaris-III, while exploring Mount Firmament, after some time, you arrive at the outskirts of Hongzhen Village. Along the way, you encounter the striking figure of a girl, who turns out to be Changli. She approaches you to talk and ask you a few questions.</strong></span></p></li></ul><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(129, 255, 188)\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/bf1bcb30-f696-41cc-8d22-697b3bb24a93_47445583-543e-4d07-bc81-66a6b5e42262.webp?width=1000\"></span></p><hr><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>If there is anything that could be improved, </strong><span style=\"color: rgb(203, 255, 255)\"><strong><em>please let me know in the feedback.</em></strong></span></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/bf1bcb30-f696-41cc-8d22-697b3bb24a93_39aaf0d5-9746-4545-ab96-c89c8527f3b3.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"bf1bcb30-f696-41cc-8d22-697b3bb24a93_007ce7bb-3108-45d3-8318-f181908c281f.webp","creator":"xIFeitan","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","📚 Fictional","🎮 Game","⛓️ Dominant","❤️‍🩹 Fluff"],"chats":4270,"messages":90412,"created_at":"2024-06-30T22:36:41.329010+00:00"}